  }, "v6"), mdx("p", null, "Sau c\xF9ng \xF4ng ch\u1EE7 ch\u1EC9 c\xF2n c\xF3 m\u1ED9t ng\u01B0\u1EDDi c\xF3 th\u1EC3 sai \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c, \u0111\xF3 l\xE0 con trai y\xEAu d\u1EA5u c\u1EE7a m\xECnh. \xD4ng sai con \u0111i v\xE0 ngh\u0129 b\u1EE5ng, 'C\xF3 l\u1EBD ch\xFAng n\xF3 s\u1EBD n\u1EC3 con ta.' "), mdx("h6", {
