  }, "v12"), mdx("p", null, "C\xE1c l\xE3nh t\u1EE5 Do-th\xE1i hi\u1EC3u ngay l\xE0 ng\u1EE5 ng\xF4n \u1EA5y \xE1m ch\u1EC9 h\u1ECD. H\u1ECD mu\u1ED1n b\u1EAFt Ch\xFAa Gi\xEA-xu nh\u01B0ng s\u1EE3 d\xE2n ch\xFAng, n\xEAn b\u1ECF \u0111i.C\xF3 n\xEAn \u0111\xF3ng thu\u1EBF hay kh\xF4ng? "), mdx("h6", {
