  }, "v13"), mdx("p", null, "Sau \u0111\xF3 h\u1ECD cho v\xE0i ng\u01B0\u1EDDi Pha-ri-xi v\xE0 \u0111\u1EA3ng vi\xEAn H\xEA-r\u1ED1t \u0111\u1EBFn g\u1EB7p Ch\xFAa Gi\xEA-xu \u0111\u1EC3 g\xE0i b\u1EABy Ng\xE0i trong l\u1EDDi n\xF3i. "), mdx("h6", {
