    "id": "v34"
  }, "v34"), mdx("p", null, "Th\u1EA5y \xF4ng ta tr\u1EA3 l\u1EDDi kh\xF4n ngoan nh\u01B0 th\u1EBF, Ng\xE0i b\u1EA3o, \"\xD4ng hi\u1EC7n r\u1EA5t g\u1EA7n v\u1EDBi N\u01B0\u1EDBc Tr\u1EDDi.\" Sau \u0111\xF3, kh\xF4ng ai d\xE1m h\u1ECFi Ng\xE0i c\xE2u n\xE0o n\u1EEFa.Ch\xFAa C\u1EE9u Th\u1EBF l\xE0 con hay Ch\xFAa c\u1EE7a vua \u0110a-v\xEDt? "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v35"
  }, "v35"), mdx("p", null, "Khi \u0111ang d\u1EA1y d\u1ED7 trong \u0111\u1EC1n th\u1EDD th\xEC Ch\xFAa Gi\xEA-xu h\u1ECFi, \"T\u1EA1i sao c\xE1c gi\xE1o s\u01B0 lu\u1EADt b\u1EA3o Ch\xFAa C\u1EE9u Th\u1EBF l\xE0 con vua \u0110a-v\xEDt? "), mdx("h6", {
